741
01:13:40,000 --> 01:13:44,994
Now, down to the more serious business
of the day, our opening address.

742
01:13:45,040 --> 01:13:48,999
I'd like to introduce
the Reverend Walter Goodfellow...

743
01:13:49,040 --> 01:13:52,032
from the Parish of Little Wallop!

744
01:14:14,640 --> 01:14:17,234
Good evening.

745
01:14:21,160 --> 01:14:24,038
Good evening, Gentlemen...

746
01:14:25,188 --> 01:14:27,478
Ladies and Gentlemen.

747
01:14:30,040 --> 01:14:32,474
It's an honour...

748
01:14:32,520 --> 01:14:35,114
to... to deliver...

749
01:14:35,280 --> 01:14:38,272
the opening address
of the convention,

750
01:14:39,532 --> 01:14:41,555
and my subject...

751
01:14:41,600 --> 01:14:44,592
is "Cod's Mysterious Ways"...

752
01:14:45,240 --> 01:14:48,232
"God's... God's Mysterious Ways",

753
01:14:49,280 --> 01:14:53,159
I'm sorry,
I'm sure that Cod have mysterious ways.

754
01:14:55,800 --> 01:15:01,750
But it's the mysterious ways of God
that I wanted to talk about this evening.

755
01:15:03,360 --> 01:15:07,353
Cod will just have to wait
for their own convention.

756
01:15:09,280 --> 01:15:12,670
So! God's Mysterious Ways.

757
01:15:14,800 --> 01:15:18,395
I'm so glad we can have this little chat.

758
01:15:19,200 --> 01:15:23,318
- What have you done with Lance, Rosemary?
- You know, I prefer Rosie.

759
01:15:23,360 --> 01:15:26,318
It takes me back to my childhood.

760
01:15:26,360 --> 01:15:29,352
What have you done with Lance, Rosie?

761
01:15:29,400 --> 01:15:32,392
- Who the hell's Lance?
- Yes, well,

762
01:15:33,720 --> 01:15:36,712
that's the question.
You see, Lance...

763
