01:15:53,680 --> 01:15:55,750
<i>Come on to Uncle Lance.</i>

767
01:15:55,800 --> 01:16:01,477
- Who the hell is this guy? I'll kill him!
- That won't be necessary, dear.

768
01:16:01,880 --> 01:16:04,440
<i>My Lord.
They're just llke llttle rose petals.</i>

769
01:16:04,480 --> 01:16:05,549
What?

