01:16:22,560 --> 01:16:25,154
That was your lover.

775
01:16:27,960 --> 01:16:31,953
- That was your lover?
- Now, you've got to understand, Holly,

776
01:16:32,080 --> 01:16:35,231
your mother's been very unhappy,
and Ionely. Well, you know,

777
01:16:35,280 --> 01:16:40,229
your father, well, he's a busy man,
and along comes this handsome American...

778
01:16:40,280 --> 01:16:45,752
with his accent and his swing,
not the type I would approve of at all.

779
01:16:45,920 --> 01:16:49,879
